      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Emissione sequenze di controllo per una linea             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-lin-stp-amp = Ampiezza linea da stampare       *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-lin-stp-inx = Indice linea da stampare         *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-lin-stp-cnt = Contenuto linea da stampare      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       emi-seq-lin-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Posizionamento al punto verticale, espresso     *
      *              * in 720mi di pollice                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Trasformazione margine superiore da formato *
      *                  * in 72mi di pollice a formato in 720mi di    *
      *                  * pollice, sottraendo l'area non stampabile   *
      *                  * superiore                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-for-msu-72p        to   w-for-n62-00a          .
           subtract  w-for-nsu-72p        from w-for-n62-00a          .
           multiply  10                   by   w-for-n62-00a          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Calcolo spostamento verticale in 72mi di    *
      *                  * pollice e quindi trasformazione in 720mi    *
      *                  * di pollice                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-lin-stp-inx        to   w-for-n62-00b          .
           multiply  w-for-pas-v72        by   w-for-n62-00b          .
           multiply  10                   by   w-for-n62-00b          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Calcolo spostamento verticale totale in     *
      *                  * 720mi di pollice, ed editing, ottenendo:    *
      *                  *  - Lunghezza del valore editato             *
      *                  *  - Valore editato allineato a sinistra      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-for-n62-00a        to   w-edt-num-str-num      .
           add       w-for-n62-00b        to   w-edt-num-str-num      .
           perform   edt-num-str-000      thru edt-num-str-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-edt-num-str-num    to   w-lin-stp-yyy          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lunghezza della sequenza                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      04                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
           add       w-edt-num-str-lun    to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sequenza                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           string    w-c0c-ESC  delimited by   size
                     "&a"       delimited by   size
                     w-edt-num-str-edt
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "V"        delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione sequenza                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-wrt-000      thru fil-bin-wrt-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se status stampa ad errore : uscita         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-err                not  =  spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-999.
       emi-seq-lin-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Posizionamento al punto orizzontale, espresso   *
      *              * in 720mi di pollice                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Trasformazione margine sinistro da formato  *
      *                  * in 72mi di pollice a formato in 720mi di    *
      *                  * pollice, sottraendo l'area non stampabile   *
      *                  * sinistra, ed editing, ottenendo:            *
      *                  *  - Lunghezza del valore editato             *
      *                  *  - Valore editato allineato a sinistra      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-for-msi-72p        to   w-edt-num-str-num      .
           subtract  w-for-nsi-72p        from w-edt-num-str-num      .
           multiply  10                   by   w-edt-num-str-num      .
           perform   edt-num-str-000      thru edt-num-str-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-edt-num-str-num    to   w-lin-stp-xxx          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lunghezza della sequenza                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      04                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
           add       w-edt-num-str-lun    to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sequenza                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           string    w-c0c-ESC  delimited by   size
                     "&a"       delimited by   size
                     w-edt-num-str-edt
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "H"        delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione sequenza                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-wrt-000      thru fil-bin-wrt-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se status stampa ad errore : uscita         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-err                not  =  spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-999.
       emi-seq-lin-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale riga grigia                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da generare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su numero linea                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin                <    06
                     go to emi-seq-lin-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su contenuto linea                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt (08 : 14)
                                          =    "--------------"
                     go to emi-seq-lin-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se linea a spaces                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt        =    spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su apposito flag                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-rlf        =    spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-lin-stp-rlf
                     go to emi-seq-lin-400.
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-stp-rlf          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su contenuto linea                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt (08 : 14)
                                          =    spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Posizionamento del cursone                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-lay-pag-mdp          .
           move      0250                 to   w-lay-pag-xnu          .
           move      w-lin-stp-yyy        to   w-lay-pag-ynu          .
           subtract  0090                 from w-lay-pag-ynu          .
           perform   emi-lay-pag-pos-000  thru emi-lay-pag-pos-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Rettangolo                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      2100                 to   w-lay-pag-xnu          .
           move      0045                 to   w-lay-pag-ynu          .
           move      "2"                  to   w-lay-pag-shd          .
           move      "10"                 to   w-lay-pag-shp          .
           perform   emi-lay-pag-ret-000  thru emi-lay-pag-ret-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ri-posizionamento del cursone               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-lay-pag-mdp          .
           move      w-lin-stp-xxx        to   w-lay-pag-xnu          .
           move      w-lin-stp-yyy        to   w-lay-pag-ynu          .
           perform   emi-lay-pag-pos-000  thru emi-lay-pag-pos-999    .
       emi-seq-lin-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa della linea                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da eseguire                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt (01 : 15)
                                          =    "===============" or
                     w-lin-stp-cnt (01 : 15)
                                          =    "---------------"
                     go to emi-seq-lin-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuale pulizia fincature                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Barre verticali                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           inspect   w-lin-stp-cnt    replacing
                                          all "|"
                                          by  " "                     .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt (22 : 12)
                                          =    "------------" or
                     w-lin-stp-cnt (22 : 12)
                                          =    "Codice e des" or
                     w-lin-stp-cnt (22 : 12)
                                          =    "-+----------"
                     move  spaces         to   w-lin-stp-cnt          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lunghezza della sequenza                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-lin-stp-amp        to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sequenza                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           string    w-lin-stp-cnt (1 : w-fil-bin-wrt-lun)
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione sequenza                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-wrt-000      thru fil-bin-wrt-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se status stampa ad errore : uscita         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-err                not  =  spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-999.
       emi-seq-lin-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     emi-seq-lin-999.
       emi-seq-lin-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
