      *                          * Lunghezza della sequenza            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      05                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
           add       w-lay-pag-xlu        to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
           add       w-lay-pag-ylu        to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
