           string    w-c0c-ESC  delimited by   size
                     "*p"       delimited by   size
                     w-lay-pag-xal
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "x"        delimited by   size
                     w-lay-pag-yal
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "Y"        delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad emissione sequenza                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     emi-lay-pag-pos-800.
       emi-lay-pag-pos-500.
